# Docusaurus docs (apps/DOCS)

## Location

- App: `apps/DOCS` (Nx project **DOCS**)
- Content: `apps/DOCS/docs/` — Docusaurus v3
- Config: `docusaurus.config.ts`, `sidebars.ts`

## Commands

```bash
pnpm nx serve DOCS    # :4001 (BE uses :3000)
pnpm nx build DOCS      # onBrokenLinks: 'throw' — run after link changes
```

## When to update

| Repo change | Doc file |
| ----------- | -------- |
| Setup / deps / Docker | `docs/setup/NN-*.md` |
| FE / BE / MongoDB | `docs/apps/frontend.md`, `backend.md`, `mongodb.md` |
| AI policy | `docs/ai/policy.md` + root `AI.md` |
| Husky / CI | `docs/setup/09-husky-quality-gates.md` + `intro.md` |
| Git branches / commitlint | `docs/setup/10-git-branches-commits.md` |

## Conventions

- Frontmatter: `sidebar_position`, optional `slug`
- Categories: `_category_.json` per folder
- Root `README.md` stays short — detailed setup belongs here, not README
- Do **not** recreate root `docs/setup.md`

## Delegate

Multi-page doc updates → `Use the docs-maintainer subagent to sync Docusaurus docs for [change]`
